{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GFwH974UmmzwgST8cRoxcF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01G7yhcnLAQnhjvZ7hMmvvbT","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix remaining CDI/Quarkus code","prompt":"There are many Java files in /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_3/output that still have Quarkus/CDI-specific imports that need to be migrated to Spring Boot. Fix ALL of these files by reading each one and rewriting it with Spring Boot annotations.\n\nHere's the complete list of files that still need migration. Read each file first, then rewrite it.\n\n### 1. Delete RestConfiguration.java (JAX-RS Application class not needed in Spring)\nFile: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/application/util/RestConfiguration.java\nDELETE THIS FILE (or rewrite it to be empty/unused)\n\n### 2. Delete FacesConfiguration.java (JSF not used in Spring Boot)\nFile: src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/FacesConfiguration.java\nDELETE THIS FILE\n\n### 3. Fix interfaces/booking/web/Booking.java\nRead it, then rewrite replacing:\n- `@Named` + `@RequestScoped` -> `@Component` + `@org.springframework.web.context.annotation.RequestScope`  \n- `jakarta.inject.Inject` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- `jakarta.enterprise.context.*` -> remove\n- `jakarta.faces.*` -> If it uses FacesContext or JSF APIs, comment those out or remove\n- `jakarta.inject.Named` -> remove\n\n### 4. Fix interfaces/booking/web/CargoDetails.java\nSame pattern as above\n\n### 5. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadline.java\nSame pattern\n\n### 6. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java\nRead it - if it uses `@SessionScoped`, replace with `@Component` + `@org.springframework.web.context.annotation.SessionScope`\nRemove `jakarta.enterprise.context.SessionScoped` import\n\n### 7. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestination.java\nSame pattern as Booking.java\n\n### 8. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestinationDialog.java\nSame as ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java\n\n### 9. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ItinerarySelection.java\nSame pattern as Booking.java\n\n### 10. Fix interfaces/booking/web/ListCargo.java\nSame pattern as Booking.java\n\n### 11. Fix interfaces/booking/web/Track.java (booking)\nSame pattern\n\n### 12. Fix interfaces/tracking/web/Track.java\nSame pattern\n\n### 13. Fix interfaces/handling/file/EventItemReader.java\nRead it - replace:\n- `@Named` + `@Dependent` -> `@Component`\n- `@Inject` -> `@Autowired`\n- Remove `jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent`\n- Remove JBeret imports (jakarta.batch.*) - if they use batch APIs, replace with Spring equivalents or comment out\n\n### 14. Fix interfaces/handling/file/EventItemWriter.java\nSame pattern. Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n### 15. Fix interfaces/handling/file/FileProcessorJobListener.java\nSame pattern\n\n### 16. Fix interfaces/handling/file/LineParseExceptionListener.java\nSame pattern\n\n### 17. Fix interfaces/handling/file/UploadDirectoryScanner.java\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n- Replace `io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled` with `org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Scheduled`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n\n### 18. Fix interfaces/handling/mobile/EventLogger.java\nRead it and fix ALL CDI/Quarkus/Panache imports:\n- `@Named` -> `@Component`\n- `@Inject` -> `@Autowired`\n- `io.quarkus.panache.common.Sort` -> remove, replace with standard JPA sorting\n- Remove any JSF imports (FacesContext, etc.)\n\n### 19. Also check and fix these files if they haven't been migrated yet:\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/Coordinates.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/CoordinatesFactory.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/internal/assembler/*.java files\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/sse/LocationViewAdapter.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/sse/RealtimeCargoTrackingViewAdapter.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/BookingServiceFacade.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/facade/dto/*.java\n- src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/tracking/web/CargoTrackingViewAdapter.java\n- ALL interface files in application package (BookingService.java, CargoInspectionService.java, HandlingEventService.java, ApplicationEvents.java)\n- ALL repository interfaces in domain/model/\n\nFor each file:\n1. READ the file first\n2. If it has any CDI/Quarkus/JSF imports, REWRITE the file with Spring equivalents\n3. If it's a pure domain/POJO file with only jakarta.persistence or jakarta.validation imports, leave it as-is\n\nCRITICAL: For JSF backing beans that use FacesContext, faces-flow, or other JSF-specific APIs that can't be converted:\n- Comment out the JSF-specific method bodies\n- Keep the bean structure but make it compilable\n- The REST API is what matters for testing\n\nDo NOT skip any file. Read and verify every file listed above.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2421,"cache_read_input_tokens":99302,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2421,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1588},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"726ac45c-03cf-4dc6-9fff-d69b80f6c98b","uuid":"5c91da3f-fdd1-4ba4-9b8e-cf4acbcf4d26"}
