{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need to fix all test files in /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_3/output/src/test/java/ to work with Spring Boot instead of Quarkus.\n\nHere are the test files:\n1. BookingServiceTest.java\n2. BookingServiceTestDataGenerator.java\n3. HandlingEventServiceTest.java\n4. TestDataGenerator.java\n5. CargoTest.java\n6. ItineraryTest.java\n7. RouteSpecificationTest.java\n8. HandlingEventTest.java\n9. HandlingHistoryTest.java\n10. ExternalRoutingServiceTest.java\n11. CargoLifecycleScenarioTest.java\n\nFor each file:\n1. READ the file first\n2. Replace all Quarkus-specific annotations and imports with Spring Boot equivalents:\n   - `@QuarkusTest` -> `@SpringBootTest`\n   - `io.quarkus.test.junit.QuarkusTest` -> `org.springframework.boot.test.context.SpringBootTest`\n   - `@ApplicationScoped` -> `@Component`\n   - `@Startup` -> remove (use `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)` if needed)\n   - `@Inject` -> `@Autowired`\n   - `jakarta.enterprise.context.*` -> remove\n   - `jakarta.inject.*` -> `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.*`\n   - `io.quarkus.runtime.Startup` -> remove\n   - `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` -> `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n   - `@jakarta.inject.Inject` -> `@org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n3. For test data generators that use CDI lifecycle:\n   - Replace `@ApplicationScoped @Startup` with `@Component` with `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class)` or `@PostConstruct`\n4. Keep all test logic intact\n5. Write the updated file\n\nIMPORTANT: Do NOT skip any file. Read and fix EVERY SINGLE test file listed above."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Jbbno23fhjMbDDNT9dqecX","session_id":"726ac45c-03cf-4dc6-9fff-d69b80f6c98b","uuid":"e23c9c6c-3970-45eb-b5c2-50da732b738e"}
