{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Ay7qh6L9BCaTA9RefpVaNC","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01CLaJYLpEvBtbPJnGcBG5RL","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix Logger injection issues","prompt":"In the project at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__quarkus__spring/run_3/output, several files still have `@Autowired private Logger logger;` which won't work in Spring (Logger is not a bean). I need you to fix ALL of these files.\n\nThe files that need fixing:\n1. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/EventItemReader.java\n2. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/FileProcessorJobListener.java\n3. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/file/LineParseExceptionListener.java\n4. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/tracking/web/Track.java\n\nAlso check these files for the same issue:\n5. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/Booking.java\n6. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/Track.java\n7. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadline.java\n8. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestination.java\n9. src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ItinerarySelection.java\n\nFor each file:\n1. READ the file\n2. Replace `@Autowired private Logger logger;` or `@Autowired private transient Logger logger;` with `private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(ClassName.class.getName());`\n3. Remove the `@Autowired` annotation from the Logger field\n4. Make sure the import is `java.util.logging.Logger`\n5. Write the file back\n\nCRITICAL: Read every file before editing. Fix every instance of injected Logger.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_